'''Mirko Dragolioub Popovich''' (yavutse 1948), ni umukinnyi wa firime wo mu Bubiligi . <ref name="cinergie">https://www.cinergie.be/personne/popovitch-mirko-dragolioub</ref> Azwi cyane nk'umuyobozi wa film izwi cyane ''Tango Ya Ba Wendo''. <ref>https://bx1.be/news/le-bonus-des-acteurs-de-bruxelles-mirko-popovitch-raconte-son-confinement/</ref>

== Ubuzima bwite ==
Yavutse mu 1948 i Buruseli mu [[Ububiligi|Bubiligi]] kandi akomoka muri [[Yugosilaviya]] . <ref>http://africultures.com/personnes/?no=10410&utm_source=newsletter&utm_medium=email&utm_campaign=479</ref> <ref>http://www.film-documentaire.fr/4DACTION/w_liste_generique/C_12619_F</ref>

== Umwuga ==
Niwe washinze kandi akaba n'umuyobozi mukuru wa 'Zinneke Parade' i Buruseli. Mu 1993, yakoze documentaire ngufi ''Tango Ya Ba Wendo'' hamwe na Roger Kwami Zinga wo muri Repubulika Iharanira Demokarasi ya Kongo . Amagambo magufi avuga ku buzima bwintangiriro yumuziki wa Zairian, Wendo, uzwi kandi nka Papa Wendo. <ref>https://www.cinergie.be/actualites/tango-ya-ba-wendo-de-mirko-popovitch</ref> Kuva 1966 kugeza 1980, Popovitch yakoraga nk'umucuranzi mumatsinda ya rock. Yakomeje gukora nk'umuyobozi ushinzwe ikigo ndangamuco cya Watermael - Boitsfort imyaka 28. Mu 1997, yabaye komiseri ushinzwe ibikorwa bya ''Na Nga Def Senegal'', aho yaje gukorera ''Laafi Burkina Faso'' mu 1999 na ''Alafia Benin'' mu 2004. 

Usibye sinema, ni n'umwanditsi mwinshi. Mu 2004, yanditse kandi asohora inkuru ngufi zatsindiye igihembo cya mbere cya Francité mu 2004 hanyuma yegukana igihembo cya RTBF Fureur de lire 2004. Mu mwaka wa 2008, yatorewe kuba Umuyobozi w’umuryango udaharanira inyungu Africalia, aho yakomereje imyaka 7 hanyuma asezera ku ya 1 Mutarama 2013. Hamwe n'uburambe bwose yabonye muri iyi myaka, yatangije umurongo wa documentaire yakozwe nabakinnyi ba firime nyafurika kubijyanye numuco. 

